data.description: Welcoming you to Perry township is this very well maintained 4 bed/2.5 bath home that was built in 2018. You will notice the covered front porch, 6' bump out on then garage, fully fenced backyard, patio and gazebo. Inside you have a spacious office, living room that is open to the dining room, and kitchen which allows for ease of entertaining. Kitchen offers an oversized pantry, and staggered cabinets. Main level laundry and utility closet. All utilities are original- 2018. Upstairs you have a loft and 4 spacious bedrooms. The primary bedroom boats a large walk-in closet, private bathroom with dual vanity, linen closet, and tub/shower combo. This home has a whole house water filtration system and heated garage as well.
